Exploration des donnes LUCAS_LUC

In[1]:
from LUC_viz import compare_LCTYPE, project_bbox
import xarray as xr

# Get historical data from the beginning
ds_1950 = xr.open_dataset("data\\LUC_hist_NA\\LUCAS_LUC_v1.1_historical_NorthAmerica_0.1deg_1950_1959.nc")
ds_2010 = xr.open_dataset("data\\LUC_hist_NA\\LUCAS_LUC_v1.1_historical_NorthAmerica_0.1deg_2010_2015.nc")

# Get projected data based on SSP2 4.5 for 2016 and 2100
ds_ssp245_2015 = xr.open_dataset("data\\LUC_future_NA\\LUCAS_LUC_v1.1_ssp245_NorthAmerica_0.1deg_2016_2025.nc")
ds_ssp245_2096 = xr.open_dataset("data\\LUC_future_NA\\LUCAS_LUC_v1.1_ssp245_NorthAmerica_0.1deg_2096_2100.nc")

volution des fractions de couverture du terrain de catgorie "Evergreen coniferous trees"

volution dans les donnes historiques (1950 2015)

    ds2 = ds_2010, time2 = "2015-01-01", 
    lctype = 5, bbox = project_bbox
